title: Bioengineers create first online search engine for functional genomics data

title_detail.value: Bioengineers create first online search engine for functional genomics data

summary: Bioengineers have created what they believe to be the first online search engine for functional genomics data. This new search engine, called GeNemo, is free for public use at: http://www.genemo.org.
